To dowload ECMWF:

Go to the ECMWF website, and login (or register for an account):
http://www.ecmwf.int/

Navigate to the MARS data retrieval interface (ECMWF Public Datasets web interface) for ERA-Interim:
http://apps.ecmwf.int/datasets/data/interim-full-daily/

Select the month you would like to download.

Select step 0 (limits the results to only analyzed fields | http://www.ecmwf.int/en/faq/what-are-steps-surface-daily-fields-era-interim).

Select all four times (0,6,12,18).

Select "surface pressure".

Download netCDF (may need to rename the long gibberish names after download is complete).
